To get trigger efficiency on EC for SIDIS (electron trigger):

double Get_SIDIS_trigger_efficiency_EC(TString det_ID,TString pid,double hit_R, double hit_Mom, bool Is_debug){
	//det_ID="large", "forward"
	//pid="electron", "gamma", "pion", "proton"
	//hit_R: r value for the hit, in cm  
	//hit_Mom: momentum of the hit
	
SIDIS FAEC Electron trigger Assumption
trig_eff (P>Max)=trig_eff(P=Max)
trig_eff (P<Min)=0
trig_eff_Proton = 0.5*trig_eff_pion

SIDIS LAEC Electron trigger Assumption
trig_eff (P>Max)=trig_eff(P=Max)
trig_eff (P<Min)=0
trig_eff_Proton = 0.5*trig_eff_pion


